Bernanke Says Fed ‘Doing What It Can’ to Cooperate With ECB

-- B y   C h r i s   W e l l i s z
-- 
2011-10-04T14:39:30Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-04/bernanke-says-fed-doing-what-it-can-to-cooperate-with-ecb.html
Federal Reserve Chairman  Ben S.
Bernanke  said the Fed is “doing what it can” to cooperate with
the  European Central Bank  as it seeks to protect the continent’s
banks amid a sovereign debt crisis.
  He was responding to questions before the Joint Economic
Committee of Congress.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
